<gmd:abstract>             <gco:CharacterString>The ports (NTAD 2014) are politically defined by port limits or Corps projects, excluding non-Corps projects not authorized for publication. The determination for the published Principal Ports is based upon the total tonnage for the port for the particular year; therefore the top 150 list can vary from year to year.</gco:CharacterString>          </gmd:abstract>          <gmd:purpose>             <gco:CharacterString>The Principal Port file contains USACE port codes, geographic locations(longitude, latitude), names, and commodity
